songs.title: What Do I Mean To You
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Keys to an open door, it don't mean a lot
Stains on a dirty floor, you don’t see a spot
What do I mean, what do I mean to you?
Waging a war inside you, but don’t see the scars
You got the moon guide you, who needs a star?
What do I mean, tell me, what do I mean to you?

[Chorus]
What do I mean to you?
What do I mean to you?
What do I, what do I mean to you?

[Verse 2]
No need for water, Rita, you got the wine
Searching for diamonds when I gave you the mine
What do I mean?
Tell me, what do I mean to you, to you?

I'm a believer, Jesus (hallelujah)
Show me the light
The side of the road, the devil gave you a ride
What do I mean?
Tell me, what do I mean to you?
Hallelujah

[Chorus]
What do I mean to you?
What do I mean to you?
What do I, what do I mean to you?

[Bridge]
A child needs a mother
And you won’t trust but not the truth
I’m just a lover
So what do I mean to you?

[Chorus]
What do I mean to you?
What do I mean to you?
What do I, what do I mean to you?
